Disadur dari [[enwiki>Large Language Model]], **//Large Language Model//** (LLM) adalah model bahasa yang mempunyai kemampuan untuk menghasilkan dan memahami bahasa untuk tujuan umum. LLM memperoleh kemampuan ini dengan mempelajari hubungan statistik dari dokumen teks selama proses pelatihan mandiri dan semi-mandiri yang intensif secara komputasi.

= ChatGPT adalah mesin pemimpi
> We direct their dreams with prompts. The prompts start the dream, and based on the LLM’s hazy recollection of its training documents, most of the time the result goes someplace useful. —[[https://twitter.com/karpathy/status/1733299213503787018?s=61&t=20jnuQQ5opsvX5aRlZ2UBg | Andrej Karpathy]]

= ChatGPT adalah permainan kata
> I can't foretell the future, but it is important to realize that ChatGPT is not artificial intelligence. It has no intelligence; it doesn't know anything and doesn't understand anything. It plays games with words to make plausible-sounding English text, but any statements made in it are liable to be false. It can't avoid that because it doesn't know what the words //mean//. —[[https://www.reddit.com/r/linux/comments/122gmm9/richard_stallmans_thoughts_on_chatgpt_artificial/?ref=share&ref_source=link | Richard Stallman]]